The package contains commands.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionCommand
    The Interface ActionCommand is template for commands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionFactory
    A factory for creating ActionCommand objects.
    AddScoresCommand
    The Class AddScoresCommand is command which adds application to database.
    ApplicationActionCommand
    The Class ApplicationActionCommand is command which shows registered application to user
    ChangeStatusCommand
    The Class ChangeStatusCommand is command which changes status of user's application
    ChooseFacultyCommand
    The Class ChooseFacultyCommand is command which shows form with part of user's data and choice of faculty.
    CreateFacultyCommand
    The Class CreateFacultyCommand is command which creates the new faculty and writes it to database
    DeleteFacultyCommand
    The Class DeleteFacultyCommand is command which allows to delete faculty from database
    EditFacultyCommand
    The Class EditFacultyCommand is command which allows to edit faculty data
    EmptyCommand
    The Class ApplicationActionCommand is command which executes if command name is empty
    FacultiesCommand  
    LangCommand
    The Class LangCommand is command which allows to switch pages' locale.
    LoginCommand
    The Class LoginCommand is command which allows to log in the system
    LogoutCommand
    The Class ApplicationActionCommand is command which allow to log out
    RegisterCommand
    The Class ApplicationActionCommand is command which allows to register new user.
    ShowAbiturientCommand
    The Class ShowAbiturientCommand is command which shows full user's application to administrator
    ShowAbiturientsListCommand
    The Class ShowAbiturientsListCommand is command which shows list of user's applications and defines who is allowed to enter the University.
    ShowFacultiesCommand
    The Class ShowFacultiesCommand is command which shows list of existing faculties
    ShowFacultyCommand
    The Class ShowFacultyCommand is command which shows list of faculties.
